    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ Strategic Territory Conquest</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mighty Kingdom</i> is a fast-paced strategy board game set in a vibrant fantasy realm, where six ancient gods—Werewolf, Ice-Dragon, Gryphin, Demon, Golem, and Treant—clash in a divine struggle for territorial control. Quick to learn but deep in strategy, each session brings new tactical opportunities and rivalries.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌐<strong>Online Multiplayer (Async)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or challenge others in <strong>asynchronous online multiplayer</strong>. Take your turn when it suits you, and compete with friends without being bound to real-time sessions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106580/extras/3a0a8a91db9c67555bb500387b65a29a.avif?t=1752834818\" width=558 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👑 Six Unique Gods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your allegiance wisely. Each of the six gods brings a distinct visual identity and thematic presence to the board. No abilities, just pure tactical dominance—every choice is yours.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧭 Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy-to-learn, hard-to-master gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable in under 30 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo mode vs. AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer with asynchronous turns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suitable for 2–6 players</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your territory by transforming fields into your domain and placing temples across the shared board. Each move is a bold leap forward—no backtracking, and enemy regions are impassable! The number of neutral buildings on a tile determines its point value, while matching colored shrines amplify your final score. In the end, the god with the largest connected domain earns powerful bonus points… and eternal glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106580/extras/96ee34b3d90fbc9376483c6d1a70254b.avif?t=1752834818\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106580/extras_big/96ee34b3d90fbc9376483c6d1a70254b.avif?t=1752834818 width=800 height=570 /></span></p>",
